@startuml
title Use Case Overview - RFID Tracking System (As-Built)

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Super Admin\n(`SUPER_ADMIN`)" as SA
actor "Admin\n(`ADMIN`)" as AD
actor "Warehouse Manager\n(`WAREHOUSE_MANAGER`)" as WM
actor "Staff\n(`STAFF`)" as ST

rectangle "RFID Tracking System" {
  usecase "UC-001\nKhởi tạo tag\nvà gán product" as UC1
  usecase "UC-002\nĐiều chuyển nội bộ\nADMIN/WORKSHOP" as UC2
  usecase "UC-003\nXuất kho\ncho khách hàng" as UC3
  usecase "UC-004\nSession và\nlive scan" as UC4
  usecase "Dashboard /\nUser /\nAudit" as UCW
}

SA --> UC2
SA --> UC3
SA --> UCW
SA --> UC1
AD --> UC1
WM --> UC2
WM --> UC3
WM --> UC4
ST --> UC4

note bottom of UC1
Implemented with /api/tags
and /api/tags/assign.
SUPER_ADMIN và ADMIN đều có thể
khởi tạo tag và gán product.
Core entity is Tag, not Asset.
end note

note bottom of UC2
Transfer types:
ADMIN_TO_WORKSHOP
WORKSHOP_TO_WAREHOUSE
Actor trong UC-002:
SUPER_ADMIN va WAREHOUSE_MANAGER.
end note

note bottom of UC3
SUPER_ADMIN hoặc WAREHOUSE_MANAGER
tạo WAREHOUSE_TO_CUSTOMER.
Transfer tạo ra COMPLETED ngay.
Neu can reverse sau do,
source hien dung admin recovery flow rieng.
end note

note bottom of UC4
scanStream may auto-create unknown EPCs.
Actor trong UC-004:
WAREHOUSE_MANAGER va STAFF la nguoi van hanh.
scanDetected di qua room scan:live;
inventoryUpdate di qua room admin:dashboard.
end note

@enduml
